translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 魔人討伐隊も出撃
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The demon extermination squad also sets out.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 狙うは魔人と魔物将軍
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Their targets are the demons and the monster generals.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 魔物隊長を倒しにがら突き進むランス達
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Lance and the others charge forward to defeat the monster captains.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: かなみの偵察で付近の魔物将軍を発見した
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Thanks to Kanami’s reconnaissance, they discovered a nearby monster general.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: その頃、北登り口
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Meanwhile, at the northern approach.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 騎士団長サーナキアあったり敗北
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Knight Commander Sanakia met with defeat.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 量産型あてな２号部隊が戦線の穴を埋める
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The mass-produced Atec No. 2 unit fills the gaps in the battle line.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 魔物将軍を倒したが
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: They defeated the monster general, but...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 中身の女の子とエッチしている暇は無い
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: There's no time to have sex with the girl inside.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 戦況を確認する為にいったん城に戻る
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: They return to the castle temporarily to check the battle situation.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ランス城司令部で戦局を聞く
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: At Lance Castle headquarters, they receive a briefing on the battle.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 芳しくない、戦力差がありすぎる
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The situation is not good; the power gap is too great.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 魔人レッドアイの居場所は依然不明
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The location of the demon Red Eye remains unknown.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: シィルと一緒に１５分だけ仮眠を取る
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: They take a 15-minute nap together with Schier.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: カフェがこっそり現れヒーリング
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Cafe secretly appears and performs healing.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: サーナキアの見舞いに行くが
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: They go to visit Sanakia in the hospital, but...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 負けたお仕置きでセックス
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: As punishment for losing, they have sex.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: "ＣＧ：サーナキアのエロ"
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: CG: Sanakia's erotic scene.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: かなみの偵察で将軍を発見
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Kanami's reconnaissance discovers a general.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: その頃、東登り口
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Meanwhile, at the eastern approach.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: リーザス親衛隊、カラー部隊の戦い
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The Lisas Royal Guard and the Color unit engage in battle.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: パステルは大規模モルルンで大活躍中に
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Pastel was doing great in a large-scale Morurun fight,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 投石に当たって負傷
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: but was hit by a stone projectile and injured.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: その頃、ランス城
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Meanwhile, at Lance Castle.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 優秀な魔物別働隊がこっそりとランス城に迫った
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: An elite monster detachment secretly approached Lance Castle.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ビスケッタさんの活躍で撃退
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Thanks to Biscetta's efforts, they were repelled.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ２体目の魔物将軍を倒した
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: They defeated the second monster general.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ランス達も疲弊してきた
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Lance and the others are also becoming exhausted.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ランス城に戻る、ビスケッタさんのお出迎え
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: They return to Lance Castle and are greeted by Biscetta.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ランス城司令部で戦局を聞く
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: At Lance Castle headquarters, they receive a battle briefing.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 魔人レッドアイの居場所は依然不明
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The whereabouts of the demon Red Eye remain unknown.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: アールコートが撤退を提案するが却下
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Alcourt proposes retreat but is rejected.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 負傷したパステルの見舞いに行くが
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: They go to visit the injured Pastel,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: いろいろ難癖つけてセックス
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: find fault with various things and have sex.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: "ＣＧ：パステルのエロ"
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: CG: Pastel's erotic scene.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: シィルと一緒に１５分だけ仮眠を取る
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: They take a 15-minute nap together with Schier.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: リアが現れるが部屋に入れる雰囲気で無かった
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Ria appears but the mood wasn't right for letting her into the room.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ランス達が出撃しようとしたら
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Just as Lance and the others are about to set out,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 正面登り口から魔人レッドアイが現れたと報告
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: They receive a report that the demon Red Eye has appeared at the main ascent.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 魔人レッドアイは、トッポス？に取り付いている
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The demon Red Eye is possessing a Topposu?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: クルックーがトッポスの説明
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Kurukku explains about Topposu.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: "コルルンサ：トッポス"
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Korurunsa: Topposu.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 兵士を吹き飛ばして快進撃を続けてきた
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: It has been blasting soldiers away and continuing its rapid advance.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 魔人レッドアイと接触
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: They come into contact with the demon Red Eye.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 戦闘開始
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Battle commences.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 戦闘中会話
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Dialogue during combat.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 魔人レッドアイトッポス
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Demon Red Eye Topposu.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 魔人レッドアイに敗北
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: They are defeated by the demon Red Eye.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 魔剣カオスを折られ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The magic sword Chaos is broken.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ランスも１０メートル吹き飛ばされ部隊全滅
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Lance is also blasted 10 meters away and the entire unit is annihilated.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ランス達が敗れ戦況は絶望的に不利
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Lance and the others are defeated and the battle situation is hopelessly unfavorable.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 魔人レッドアイ、そして魔軍の大軍を止めれない
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: They cannot stop the demon Red Eye and the vast demon army.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: コパンドンが命の危険がある究極お神籤を成功
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Copandon successfully performs the ultimate divination despite the mortal danger.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: なんとか魔人レッドアイを山の麓まで吹き飛ばした
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Somehow, they blast the demon Red Eye down to the foot of the mountain.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 気絶していたランスが目覚めた
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Lance, who had been unconscious, awakens.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 敗北したがまだ諦めてはいない
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Though defeated, he has not given up yet.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 折れたカオスをカフェが部屋に連れ込んだ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Cafe takes the broken Chaos sword into her room.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: カオスが回復中、ランスは別室で休憩していた
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: While Chaos is recovering, Lance rests in a separate room.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: レッドアイ・・より強い物に寄生する
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Red Eye... parasitizes something stronger.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 過去には要塞に寄生した事もある
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: In the past, it even parasitized a fortress.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 魔人討伐隊も出撃
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The demon extermination squad also sets out.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 狙うは魔人と魔物将軍
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Their targets are the demons and the monster generals.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 魔物隊長を倒しにがら突き進むランス達
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Lance and the others charge forward to defeat the monster captains.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: かなみの偵察で付近の魔物将軍を発見した
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Thanks to Kanami’s reconnaissance, they discovered a nearby monster general.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: その頃、北登り口
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Meanwhile, at the northern approach.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 騎士団長サーナキアあったり敗北
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Knight Commander Sanakia met with defeat.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 量産型あてな２号部隊が戦線の穴を埋める
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The mass-produced Atec No. 2 unit fills the gaps in the battle line.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 魔物将軍を倒したが
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: They defeated the monster general, but...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 中身の女の子とエッチしている暇は無い
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: There's no time to have sex with the girl inside.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 戦況を確認する為にいったん城に戻る
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: They return to the castle temporarily to check the battle situation.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ランス城司令部で戦局を聞く
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: At Lance Castle headquarters, they receive a briefing on the battle.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 芳しくない、戦力差がありすぎる
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The situation is not good; the power gap is too great.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 魔人レッドアイの居場所は依然不明
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The location of the demon Red Eye remains unknown.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: シィルと一緒に１５分だけ仮眠を取る
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: They take a 15-minute nap together with Schier.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: カフェがこっそり現れヒーリング
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Cafe secretly appears and performs healing.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: サーナキアの見舞いに行くが
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: They go to visit Sanakia in the hospital, but...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 負けたお仕置きでセックス
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: As punishment for losing, they have sex.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: "ＣＧ：サーナキアのエロ"
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: CG: Sanakia's erotic scene.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: かなみの偵察で将軍を発見
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Kanami's reconnaissance discovers a general.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: その頃、東登り口
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Meanwhile, at the eastern approach.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: リーザス親衛隊、カラー部隊の戦い
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The Lisas Royal Guard and the Color unit engage in battle.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: パステルは大規模モルルンで大活躍中に
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Pastel was doing great in a large-scale Morurun fight,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 投石に当たって負傷
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: but was hit by a stone projectile and injured.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: その頃、ランス城
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Meanwhile, at Lance Castle.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 優秀な魔物別働隊がこっそりとランス城に迫った
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: An elite monster detachment secretly approached Lance Castle.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ビスケッタさんの活躍で撃退
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Thanks to Biscetta's efforts, they were repelled.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ２体目の魔物将軍を倒した
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: They defeated the second monster general.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ランス達も疲弊してきた
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Lance and the others are also becoming exhausted.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ランス城に戻る、ビスケッタさんのお出迎え
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: They return to Lance Castle and are greeted by Biscetta.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ランス城司令部で戦局を聞く
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: At Lance Castle headquarters, they receive a battle briefing.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 魔人レッドアイの居場所は依然不明
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The whereabouts of the demon Red Eye remain unknown.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: アールコートが撤退を提案するが却下
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Alcourt proposes retreat but is rejected.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 負傷したパステルの見舞いに行くが
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: They go to visit the injured Pastel,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: いろいろ難癖つけてセックス
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: find fault with various things and have sex.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: "ＣＧ：パステルのエロ"
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: CG: Pastel's erotic scene.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: シィルと一緒に１５分だけ仮眠を取る
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: They take a 15-minute nap together with Schier.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: リアが現れるが部屋に入れる雰囲気で無かった
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Ria appears but the mood wasn't right for letting her into the room.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ランス達が出撃しようとしたら
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Just as Lance and the others are about to set out,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 正面登り口から魔人レッドアイが現れたと報告
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: They receive a report that the demon Red Eye has appeared at the main ascent.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 魔人レッドアイは、トッポス？に取り付いている
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The demon Red Eye is possessing a Topposu?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: クルックーがトッポスの説明
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Kurukku explains about Topposu.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: "コルルンサ：トッポス"
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Korurunsa: Topposu.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 兵士を吹き飛ばして快進撃を続けてきた
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: It has been blasting soldiers away and continuing its rapid advance.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 魔人レッドアイと接触
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: They come into contact with the demon Red Eye.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 戦闘開始
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Battle commences.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 戦闘中会話
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Dialogue during combat.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 魔人レッドアイトッポス
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Demon Red Eye Topposu.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 魔人レッドアイに敗北
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: They are defeated by the demon Red Eye.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 魔剣カオスを折られ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The magic sword Chaos is broken.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ランスも１０メートル吹き飛ばされ部隊全滅
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Lance is also blasted 10 meters away and the entire unit is annihilated.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ランス達が敗れ戦況は絶望的に不利
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Lance and the others are defeated and the battle situation is hopelessly unfavorable.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 魔人レッドアイ、そして魔軍の大軍を止めれない
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: They cannot stop the demon Red Eye and the vast demon army.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: コパンドンが命の危険がある究極お神籤を成功
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Copandon successfully performs the ultimate divination despite the mortal danger.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: なんとか魔人レッドアイを山の麓まで吹き飛ばした
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Somehow, they blast the demon Red Eye down to the foot of the mountain.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 気絶していたランスが目覚めた
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Lance, who had been unconscious, awakens.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 敗北したがまだ諦めてはいない
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Though defeated, he has not given up yet.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 折れたカオスをカフェが部屋に連れ込んだ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Cafe takes the broken Chaos sword into her room.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: カオスが回復中、ランスは別室で休憩していた
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: While Chaos is recovering, Lance rests in a separate room.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: レッドアイ・・より強い物に寄生する
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Red Eye... parasitizes something stronger.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 過去には要塞に寄生した事もある
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: In the past, it even parasitized a fortress.
